{"tid":1504024,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★澳門 賀一誠：「派錢」這措施多年來行之有效 不會有太大改變","createTime":"2019-08-25T07:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T07:42:24.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0e1992ccaa7af7b251ef8cc62f6dcc701b5afdaf","tid":1504024,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:21:42.000Z","msg":"被問到香港修例風波對澳門的影響，他這樣回應。<br />\n<br />\n賀一誠稱：「風波終會停止，再大的颱風都會過去。我們的導遊業、很多的行業都受到有關的影響，但我們要先做好內需工作，我們自己與其他(大灣區)九個城市合作的工作，不會因為某一事件而拖慢，這個我們會加快。」<br />\n<br />\n至於上任後會否「派錢」，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他說這措施多年來行之有效</span></span></strong>，對基層有幫忙，相信不會有太大改變。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5d6222f4e60383463c678e46/%E8%B3%80%E4%B8%80%E8%AA%A0%E4%BB%A5392%E7%A5%A8%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E9%95%B7%E5%AE%98-%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E8%BE%A6%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E7%A5%9D%E8%B3%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5d6222f4e60383463c678e46%2F%25E8%25B3%2580%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E4%25BB%25A5392%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E7%2595%25B6%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25BA%2594%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E7%25A5%259D%25E8%25B3%2580&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1DpzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=f2b9ef34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5d6222f4e60383463c678e46/%E8%B3%80%E4%B8%80%E8%AA%A0%E4%BB%A5392%E7%A5%A8%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E9%95%B7%E5%AE%98-%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E8%BE%A6%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E7%A5%9D%E8%B3%80</a>"},{"pid":"856f8e6dcdfe4b4ecdfa063ab5911917139cf5b2","tid":1504024,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkg